{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"264","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"川普不做，我們有責！ 彭博捐1.33億元阻氣候變遷","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>英國廣播公司報導，前紐約市長<a href='https://udn.com/search/tagging/2/%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A' rel='107229' style='color: rgb(0, 84, 166); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none;'><span style='color: rgb(136, 136, 136); text-decoration-line: underline;'>彭博</span></a>說，將提供450萬美元（約台幣1.33億元），以彌補美國對<a href='https://udn.com/search/tagging/2/%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E6%B0%A3%E5%80%99%E5%8D%94%E5%AE%9A' rel='118066' style='color: rgb(0, 84, 166); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none;'><span style='color: rgb(136, 136, 136); text-decoration-line: underline;'>巴黎氣候協定</span></a>的財政承諾責任。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>彭博自認有責任協助改善環境，因為美國總統川普去年6月宣布，他決定退出該協定，引爆國際社會的譴責。此舉將使美國實質上成為唯一不參加巴黎氣候協定的國家。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro 